g.text: Each client can have this exact coversation at the same moment.
LoginOK = LoginFirst( String Username, Int LobbySize ) [RMI]
When we reach the LobbySize set from the first player the Server starts the game, the Server autonomously draw the Goal_Cards and set the Board.
DrawValid = askDraw( string username, int a, int b ) [RMI]
putValid = askPutItem( int a, int b, int c, int col ) [RMI]
IF THE GAME ENDS, THE SCORE AND THE WINNER ARE SHOWN.
THE CLIENT HAS THE ONLY OPTION TO SHUTDOWN.
